she's a neutron bomb.

25:29.779 --> 25:31.113
<i>I thought you were blond.</i>

25:31.197 --> 25:33.074
<i>No, honey. I'm not blond.</i>

25:33.157 --> 25:35.701
<i>Did you think that I was a dumb blond?</i>

25:36.410 --> 25:38.829
<i>Honey, don't underestimate me.</i>

25:39.580 --> 25:41.624
<i>I can do so many things.</i>

25:53.636 --> 25:55.846
Tota, is everything okay?

25:56.138 --> 25:58.975
