29:10.583 --> 29:13.002
I was told it's the birthday boy's turn.

29:13.878 --> 29:15.212
Will you come with me?

29:27.099 --> 29:28.476
Happy Birthday!

29:39.028 --> 29:41.280
Pelusa isn't here. He's out.

29:41.780 --> 29:43.365
I wanted to give him a gift.

29:43.449 --> 29:46.744
When he gets back, he'll go to bed
because he has practice.

29:48.454 --> 29:49.705
