29:52.458 --> 29:55.503
Listen, forget about Pelusa, okay?

29:56.545 --> 29:58.380
He has to focus on soccer.

29:58.464 --> 30:00.090
Diego says he likes being with me.

30:00.174 --> 30:02.885
What I say matters, not Diego's words.

30:12.937 --> 30:14.813
