31:14.248 --> 31:16.792
Don't worry, they'll forget soon enough.

31:56.206 --> 32:00.961
<i>Ladies and gentlemen,</i>
<i>the moment we've been waiting for.</i>

32:01.086 --> 32:03.047
<i>Maradona's here.</i>

32:03.130 --> 32:05.382
<i>Boca's here.</i>

32:05.466 --> 32:09.678
<i>Diego Armando Maradona is here.</i>

32:13.724 --> 32:16.185
<i>Number 10 is making his debut today,</i>

32:16.268 --> 32:18.103
<i>wearing the Boca jersey.</i>

32:18.187 --> 32:20.731
<i>-His family is happy.</i>
