32:33.243 --> 32:35.079
<i>There goes Maradona.</i>

32:35.579 --> 32:40.834
<i>A penalty. Maradona shoots! Goal!</i>

32:41.251 --> 32:46.882
<i>Goal by Boca!</i>

32:46.965 --> 32:49.510
