32:49.593 --> 32:52.805
<i>For Diego's debut,</i>
<i>it's Boca, four, Talleres, one.</i>

32:52.888 --> 32:55.641
<i>Are you awake</i>
<i>or did you fall asleep, honey?</i>

32:55.724 --> 32:59.478
No, Moni, how could I fall asleep?
I'm here.

33:42.980 --> 33:46.442
You know what my present will be
for the goals you scored?

33:46.525 --> 33:48.610
