<i>because it's a surprise.</i>

34:46.168 --> 34:49.379
<i>-Good morning.</i>
<i>-Get out.</i>

34:49.463 --> 34:52.925
<i>Come on, wake up!</i>
<i>I have a surprise for you.</i>

