36:09.459 --> 36:12.588
Shall we? That's it.

36:17.718 --> 36:19.052
Mommy!

36:19.761 --> 36:21.763
- Are you okay?
- Grandma!

36:27.185 --> 36:28.687
Don't lie to us.

36:29.187 --> 36:32.357
- Dad's dead?
