36:32.441 --> 36:35.110
I'm sick of being treated
like everyone else!

36:35.485 --> 36:36.904
I know Dad's dead.

36:37.195 --> 36:40.574
- That's why the police is here.
- No, that's not true.

36:40.657 --> 36:42.034
It's something else.

36:42.868 --> 36:46.747
