36:58.467 --> 36:59.968
so he'll be fine.

37:01.094 --> 37:04.681
- Stay calm, okay?
- Okay.

37:14.066 --> 37:15.359
How are you?

37:15.442 --> 37:16.777
How are you, guys?

37:20.864 --> 37:23.784
Just came by to say hi.

37:23.867 --> 37:26.536
