40:10.033 --> 40:11.451
<i>It's his first year in Boca.</i>

40:11.535 --> 40:15.539
<i>Diego Armando Maradona's</i>
<i>on the front page of every newspaper.</i>

40:15.622 --> 40:17.916
<i>Not just in Argentina,</i>
<i>but the entire world.</i>

40:17.999 --> 40:19.918
<i>Everyone praises Diego.</i>

40:20.001 --> 40:21.378
<i>Boca's the champion.</i>

40:21.461 --> 40:25.715
<i>Boca team, lead by Silvio Marzolini,</i>
<i>has great stars.</i>

40:25.799 --> 40:29.010
<i>And this was key in decisive games.</i>

40:30.804 --> 40:34.266
<i>Against Ferro, they won 1-0</i>
<i>with a goal by Perotti.</i>

40:39.646 --> 40:40.689
<i>There goes Diego.</i>

40:40.772 --> 40:45.944
<i>There goes Maradona, goal for Boca!</i>

40:46.361 --> 40:48.113
<i>Diego Armando Maradona.</i>

40:48.196 --> 40:50.991
Great expectations,
Boca's going for the championship.

40:51.074 --> 40:54.202
<i>Penalty for Boca. He moves, he shoots...</i>

40:54.286 --> 40:59.374
<i>Goal for Boca!</i>

40:59.457 --> 41:02.502
<i>La Bombonera is about to explode.</i>
<i>Boca wins!</i>

41:02.586 --> 41:04.421
<i>They win the 1981 championship.</i>

41:06.256 --> 41:08.425
